WEBVTT

00:16.830 --> 00:17.640
Mother,

00:18.350 --> 00:20.280
you're airing out the books again.

00:21.000 --> 00:23.120
This time, I'm not airing out the books.

00:23.120 --> 00:24.350
In fact, I'm taking all of them

00:24.350 --> 00:25.030
away.

00:25.380 --> 00:26.780
Are you leaving, Mother?

00:28.960 --> 00:30.290
What makes you say that?

00:30.350 --> 00:32.280
You love books as much as your life.

00:32.280 --> 00:33.680
If the books are leaving,

00:33.880 --> 00:35.710
then you must be leaving too.

00:35.790 --> 00:37.190
You're very smart, Ziqi.

00:37.640 --> 00:38.770
But don't you worry.

00:39.110 --> 00:41.240
I'm just moving to another place.

00:41.640 --> 00:43.030
I'll still come back from time to time

00:43.030 --> 00:44.430
to check your homework.

00:44.920 --> 00:47.250
Do you see that box?
Your homework's in it.

00:51.240 --> 00:53.280
Ziqi, go back and get changed now.

00:53.470 --> 00:55.400
You're covered in sweat. Let's go.

01:07.760 --> 01:08.820
So you've set a day?

01:09.920 --> 01:10.920
His Highness said

01:11.230 --> 01:13.490
this courtyard would be reserved for me.

01:13.840 --> 01:15.570
I will still be Ziqi's teacher,

01:16.120 --> 01:17.780
and a member of the household.

01:19.200 --> 01:20.060
I didn't expect

01:20.710 --> 01:22.440
this day to arrive eventually.

01:23.640 --> 01:24.560
But I think

01:25.039 --> 01:27.039
it's a good thing that this day came.

01:28.280 --> 01:29.430
I remember the day

01:29.430 --> 01:31.560
when I picked you up from the He Mansion

01:32.350 --> 01:33.150
and completed

01:34.950 --> 01:37.080
the wedding with you on Wuyi's behalf.

01:37.120 --> 01:38.450
At that time, I thought,

01:38.789 --> 01:39.920
my brother was lucky

01:40.870 --> 01:42.590
to marry such a girl
as the Heir's Consort.

01:42.590 --> 01:43.400
Anmin...

01:43.509 --> 01:44.229
I know

01:44.680 --> 01:45.880
between you and Wuyi,

01:46.310 --> 01:47.200
there is trust,

01:47.920 --> 01:49.000
but never love.

01:49.950 --> 01:51.200
This is his loss.

02:05.350 --> 02:06.210
These few books

02:06.760 --> 02:08.360
are about river management.

02:08.470 --> 02:10.400
There are also some medical books.

02:10.590 --> 02:12.960
I think they might be of help to you.

02:18.560 --> 02:20.470
Yuanji, if I...

02:23.910 --> 02:25.280
If I were not Wuyi's brother,

02:25.280 --> 02:26.280
-I...
-Brother.

02:31.680 --> 02:33.490
I do not fear gossip.

02:34.310 --> 02:35.079
However,

02:35.750 --> 02:38.010
I've always seen you as a brother figure.

02:39.150 --> 02:40.630
I deem it as a blessing for me

02:40.630 --> 02:42.290
to marry into the Xiao family,

02:42.400 --> 02:44.200
to become part of the household,

02:44.710 --> 02:46.440
and to support each other here.

02:48.079 --> 02:49.480
You are always so clever,

02:51.120 --> 02:52.920
not leaving me a glimmer of hope.

02:54.560 --> 02:55.240
Never mind.

02:57.190 --> 02:58.710
Upon stepping out of this door,

02:58.710 --> 03:00.770
you'll be embraced by the vast world.

03:04.150 --> 03:06.680
I wish you all the best,
and may all your dreams

03:07.150 --> 03:07.960
come true.

04:44.100 --> 04:48.170
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

04:48.240 --> 04:51.120
[Episode 21]

04:52.030 --> 04:54.659
[Northern Qin]

04:59.190 --> 04:59.720
Quick!

05:00.720 --> 05:01.450
Keep moving!

05:05.360 --> 05:06.090
Walk faster!

05:08.160 --> 05:08.680
Quick!

05:09.830 --> 05:11.560
Get up. Get up now!

05:11.560 --> 05:12.190
Hold on!

05:15.300 --> 05:16.160
Your Highness.

05:20.190 --> 05:21.320
Princess Pingning?

05:26.600 --> 05:27.430
What a coincidence.

05:27.430 --> 05:28.020
It's not.

05:29.240 --> 05:31.040
I came specifically to find you.

05:34.360 --> 05:35.090
Get a move on!

05:35.950 --> 05:36.390
Go!

05:37.190 --> 05:37.680
Quick!

05:39.000 --> 05:40.240
Didn't you say...

05:40.870 --> 05:42.800
If you change your mind one day,

05:43.040 --> 05:44.390
come to Northern Qin to find me.

05:44.390 --> 05:45.680
My Eagle King's Mansion

05:45.680 --> 05:47.610
will always open its doors for you!

05:48.190 --> 05:49.720
Now, I am here.

05:52.830 --> 05:53.950
Are you regretting it?

05:53.950 --> 05:55.800
A beauty throws herself into my arms.

05:55.800 --> 05:56.950
How could I refuse?

05:58.510 --> 06:00.170
Pretty though this flower is,

06:00.600 --> 06:01.800
I am not sure

06:02.240 --> 06:03.160
if it is toxic.

06:07.630 --> 06:09.390
I killed Xie Jiayu's mother,

06:09.680 --> 06:11.140
namely Princess Yunzhao.

06:11.430 --> 06:13.430
I just escaped from the clutches
of Xiao Wuyi

06:13.430 --> 06:14.230
and Xie Jiayu.

06:14.870 --> 06:16.270
If I go back to Ye,

06:17.190 --> 06:18.720
all that awaits me is death.

06:19.390 --> 06:21.040
I have no home to go to now.

06:21.480 --> 06:23.540
Xiao Wuyi is a domineering dictator.

06:23.800 --> 06:24.800
My brother simply

06:24.830 --> 06:26.690
cannot put up a fight against him.

06:27.240 --> 06:28.700
But I believe that one day,

06:29.720 --> 06:31.800
my brother will definitely
go to war with him

06:31.800 --> 06:33.260
and have a final showdown.

06:33.560 --> 06:34.560
On this matter,

06:35.360 --> 06:37.960
I assume you and my brother
share the same goal.

06:38.360 --> 06:38.950
I can be

06:38.950 --> 06:40.680
a bridge between the two of you.

06:48.830 --> 06:49.270
You...

06:50.430 --> 06:51.090
Let go of...

07:22.430 --> 07:24.120
Alright. This is enough!

07:33.360 --> 07:35.090
Already packed everything up?

07:39.070 --> 07:39.750
Mother.

07:40.040 --> 07:41.830
Yuanji, over all these years,

07:42.120 --> 07:44.120
in the huge Prince Jing'an's Mansion,

07:44.120 --> 07:46.850
you've actually been the one
keeping me company.

07:47.120 --> 07:47.920
It's a shame

07:48.120 --> 07:50.250
that we are not destined to be in-laws.

07:50.830 --> 07:51.870
Wuyi aside,

07:53.510 --> 07:54.240
in fact,

07:55.470 --> 07:56.200
Anmin...

07:56.220 --> 07:56.780
Mother.

07:57.880 --> 07:59.530
I feel guilty about someone,

08:00.000 --> 08:01.660
and can never stop feeling so.

08:01.830 --> 08:03.030
My heart is burdened.

08:03.070 --> 08:04.000
Fine, forget it.

08:04.390 --> 08:07.520
The Xiao family doesn't have the luck
to keep you around.

08:08.000 --> 08:10.870
Yuanji, you're about to return home
after the divorce

08:10.870 --> 08:13.430
to solve the long-standing problems
in the He family.

08:13.430 --> 08:15.690
Once your family agrees with the reform,

08:15.750 --> 08:18.610
it will surely be attacked
by other noble families.

08:18.750 --> 08:21.210
A lot of difficulties are lying
ahead of you.

08:24.360 --> 08:25.760
If you really can't cope,

08:26.560 --> 08:27.670
just come back to us.

08:27.670 --> 08:28.600
Jinyi Courtyard

08:30.240 --> 08:31.370
will still be yours.

08:31.560 --> 08:33.020
Prince Jing'an's Mansion

08:34.320 --> 08:35.750
will always be your home.

08:37.020 --> 08:37.770
Mother...

08:40.480 --> 08:41.240
Yuanji,

08:42.240 --> 08:43.240
for so many years,

08:44.000 --> 08:45.670
I have always wanted a daughter.

08:45.670 --> 08:47.470
It's a pity that I can't have one.

08:48.040 --> 08:50.170
How about I take you as my goddaughter?

08:51.150 --> 08:54.510
From now on, we will address each other
as mother and daughter.

08:54.510 --> 08:56.570
And you will still be Ziqi's teacher.

08:57.000 --> 08:58.000
What do you think?

08:59.750 --> 09:00.950
If you deem me worthy,

09:01.360 --> 09:03.020
I'm more than willing to do so.

09:03.630 --> 09:05.960
These few years I spent
in Prince Jing'an's Mansion

09:05.960 --> 09:07.200
were the most free

09:07.440 --> 09:09.300
and unrestrained days of my life.

09:12.480 --> 09:14.740
I consider myself extremely fortunate.

09:15.880 --> 09:16.710
Please get up.

09:23.790 --> 09:24.870
Does Yuanji not plan

09:24.870 --> 09:27.000
to tell Liu Zhaolin about his origins?

09:28.750 --> 09:30.440
Empress Dowager He already found an excuse

09:30.440 --> 09:32.200
to execute the entire Pei family.

09:32.200 --> 09:33.630
Suppose Liu Zhaolin is reminded

09:33.630 --> 09:35.230
of himself being Pei Runheng

09:35.270 --> 09:37.960
right now, when He Yuanji is about to
take charge of the He family,

09:37.960 --> 09:38.960
he will come to realize

09:38.960 --> 09:40.870
that she is actually an enemy of his.

09:40.870 --> 09:42.000
Then how should

09:42.000 --> 09:43.730
the two of them face each other?

09:45.360 --> 09:47.440
Now, the Cui Family Case has been tried

09:47.440 --> 09:48.240
and reviewed.

09:49.150 --> 09:50.670
Conclusive evidence confirms

09:50.670 --> 09:51.870
that the Cui family illegally mined

09:51.870 --> 09:53.130
and brutalized women.

09:53.320 --> 09:54.870
However, Cui Jun already died.

09:54.870 --> 09:56.320
Cui Lingyi and Cui Shao'an

09:56.320 --> 09:57.960
stopped Cui Jun from destroying the fields

09:57.960 --> 09:59.150
so as to help the women escape.

09:59.150 --> 10:00.270
Their merits offset their faults.

10:00.270 --> 10:02.550
In the end, their property
was confiscated,

10:02.550 --> 10:04.880
and Cui Shao'an was reduced to a commoner.

10:06.750 --> 10:08.550
There's still mercy left in Mao.

10:10.240 --> 10:11.640
Do you no longer blame him

10:12.240 --> 10:13.440
for what Li Lejun did?

10:14.670 --> 10:17.070
You told me to handle it myself,
didn't you?

10:18.320 --> 10:19.650
This matter is over now.

10:28.270 --> 10:29.750
Actually, I have cracked the secret

10:29.750 --> 10:31.030
within the Phoenix Heart Tokens.

10:31.030 --> 10:33.690
Whether they exist or not
no longer matters now.

10:42.910 --> 10:43.600
Look.

10:45.910 --> 10:47.200
These three spots on the map

10:47.200 --> 10:49.400
are the locations of mineral deposits.

11:04.720 --> 11:06.550
This is the map my master drew

11:06.550 --> 11:08.150
after traveling all over Ye.

11:09.120 --> 11:10.600
Look at these three places here.

11:10.600 --> 11:11.720
They match the three spots

11:11.720 --> 11:13.180
on the tokens, don't they?

11:17.630 --> 11:19.360
I've asked Ye Xing to bring back

11:19.360 --> 11:21.000
water and soil from these places.

11:21.000 --> 11:23.860
Then we'll know
if there are minerals hidden there.

11:26.680 --> 11:27.470
Ye Xing?

11:28.440 --> 11:29.550
He's that Shadow Envoy.

11:29.550 --> 11:30.550
I gave him a name.

11:32.150 --> 11:33.600
I didn't mean to let him stay at first.

11:33.600 --> 11:34.670
But he said the mission of a Shadow Envoy

11:34.670 --> 11:36.400
is to protect the royal family.

11:36.440 --> 11:37.320
With Princess Yunzhao's passing,

11:37.320 --> 11:38.790
he was supposed to take his own life.

11:38.790 --> 11:39.670
If I refused to keep him around,

11:39.670 --> 11:40.800
he would have to die.

11:40.960 --> 11:42.220
That was really scary.

11:43.840 --> 11:45.270
So I had to let him stick around.

11:45.270 --> 11:46.470
I also gave him a name.

11:47.240 --> 11:47.750
I'd hate for him

11:47.750 --> 11:49.210
to end up like his brother.

11:51.120 --> 11:52.480
Is it a rule for all Shadow Envoys

11:52.480 --> 11:53.680
serving the royalty?

11:53.720 --> 11:56.870
That is, envoys have to be buried
with their dead masters.

11:56.870 --> 11:57.960
Then what about your previous...

11:57.960 --> 12:00.960
They've been trained this way
since they were little.

12:01.480 --> 12:03.510
They consider such conduct an honor.

12:03.510 --> 12:05.310
It cannot be changed overnight.

12:07.750 --> 12:08.440
Fine.

12:09.030 --> 12:11.290
Although Empress Wenxi was your mother,

12:11.360 --> 12:13.090
and Emperor Wenxi your father,

12:14.150 --> 12:15.280
I have to say they did

12:15.440 --> 12:17.170
resort to terrifying methods.

12:17.600 --> 12:19.510
They were not much better than Cui Jun.

12:19.510 --> 12:21.120
So, it is actually good for you
to forsake the post

12:21.120 --> 12:22.380
of Crown Prince Wenxi.

12:39.240 --> 12:40.700
Did you really revive him?

12:41.240 --> 12:42.910
Yes, he's also from the Beifu Army.

12:42.910 --> 12:44.270
Last year, he suffered
serious head trauma,

12:44.270 --> 12:45.670
resulting in blood stasis.

12:45.670 --> 12:46.960
His case was severer than yours.

12:46.960 --> 12:48.490
He went blind immediately.

12:48.550 --> 12:49.510
For the past year,

12:49.510 --> 12:50.910
I have been treating him.

12:51.630 --> 12:53.120
Having a strong will to live,

12:53.120 --> 12:54.390
he boldly tried every treatment

12:54.390 --> 12:55.790
and medicine available.

12:56.030 --> 12:57.750
Now, I've finally found a way

12:57.750 --> 12:59.010
to clear blood stasis.

12:59.480 --> 13:01.120
His vision is restored as we speak.

13:01.120 --> 13:02.510
With proper care,

13:03.030 --> 13:04.840
I believe he'll live for as long
as any other healthy man.

13:04.840 --> 13:05.700
What's the way?

13:06.120 --> 13:08.720
Acupuncture,
plus an incision into the skull.

13:10.440 --> 13:12.120
How many patients
have you treated this way?

13:12.120 --> 13:12.670
Three.

13:14.510 --> 13:16.440
And only this one survived, right?

13:16.840 --> 13:18.240
What about the other two?

13:18.360 --> 13:19.630
Are they dead or paralyzed?

13:19.630 --> 13:20.630
I went to great lengths

13:20.630 --> 13:21.830
to finally find a way,

13:21.870 --> 13:23.080
yet you're still being picky!

13:23.080 --> 13:24.000
You want to live, don't you?

13:24.000 --> 13:25.360
Now I've offered you a solution.

13:25.360 --> 13:26.490
If you refuse to try,

13:27.030 --> 13:28.490
then forget I ever said it.

13:30.870 --> 13:31.670
I won't try it.

13:36.200 --> 13:38.200
Your condition isn't as serious as his.

13:38.200 --> 13:40.000
The treatment won't be as risky.

13:40.030 --> 13:40.910
I can tell you for sure

13:40.910 --> 13:42.200
that I'm more confident with your case.

13:42.200 --> 13:43.120
Once cured, you won't

13:43.120 --> 13:44.390
have to worry about dying soon.

13:44.390 --> 13:45.630
I can't afford to take

13:46.510 --> 13:47.630
even the slightest risk.

13:47.630 --> 13:48.690
Neither can Beifu.

13:50.630 --> 13:51.320
Fine.

13:51.790 --> 13:53.150
Then just wait to go blind in three years

13:53.150 --> 13:54.030
and die in five.

13:54.480 --> 13:55.670
I'm off to tell Jiayu about this.

13:55.670 --> 13:57.130
I forbid you from doing so!

14:01.510 --> 14:02.910
This is a military order.

14:04.030 --> 14:05.790
Jiayu doesn't know about your condition.

14:05.790 --> 14:07.270
She's even planning to travel all over Ye

14:07.270 --> 14:08.550
to restore the mineral map.

14:08.550 --> 14:09.670
Can you bear to see that happen?

14:09.670 --> 14:11.270
She's doing it for Princess Yunzhao,

14:11.270 --> 14:12.600
and also for fulfilling

14:12.720 --> 14:14.600
her own wish of exploring the world.

14:14.600 --> 14:16.030
There isn't much time
left for you already.

14:16.030 --> 14:16.270
You can...

14:16.270 --> 14:17.080
Why even wait?

14:17.720 --> 14:18.550
So she'll finally

14:18.550 --> 14:20.210
have freedom only after I die?

14:21.120 --> 14:21.750
What if I'm in luck

14:21.750 --> 14:23.030
and still alive five years later?

14:23.030 --> 14:24.440
How can I ask her to just stick around

14:24.440 --> 14:26.100
and be with me the entire time?

14:31.630 --> 14:33.560
Xie Jiayu has her own path to tread.

14:46.750 --> 14:48.350
Has it ever crossed your mind

14:48.440 --> 14:50.510
that Jiayu will figure out the truth
eventually?

14:50.510 --> 14:51.910
What will she think then?

14:52.720 --> 14:54.390
If your condition worsens
faster than anticipated,

14:54.390 --> 14:55.960
leaving you
with less than three to five years,

14:55.960 --> 14:58.510
she will hate you
when she returns from her travels

14:58.510 --> 15:00.310
only to find you dead, won't she?

15:04.200 --> 15:05.000
Right?

15:07.600 --> 15:08.240
Xiao Wuyi.

15:09.270 --> 15:10.320
I was talking to you.

15:10.320 --> 15:11.180
Did you hear me?

15:12.320 --> 15:12.980
What was it?

15:15.200 --> 15:16.030
I said,

15:16.200 --> 15:18.440
Cangshan is very close
to Beifu's Yunzhong Camp.

15:18.440 --> 15:19.970
Can I have a short stay there

15:20.320 --> 15:21.250
if I ever pass by?

15:28.870 --> 15:29.750
Of course.

15:30.240 --> 15:32.970
You're now family
with a member of the Beifu Army.

15:44.440 --> 15:45.900
Do remember to write to me.

15:46.770 --> 15:48.700
You just focus on the Beifu Reform.

15:52.000 --> 15:53.030
I'll go find you.

15:55.240 --> 15:58.270
It won't take much time
to defeat Northern Qin, Xiao Wuyi.

15:58.270 --> 15:58.910
Trust me.

15:59.840 --> 16:01.750
I'll definitely find the mineral deposits

16:01.750 --> 16:02.960
and produce caltrop fireballs

16:02.960 --> 16:04.160
for you and my master.

16:06.540 --> 16:11.170
♪ Hear the heartbeat by my side ♪

16:12.370 --> 16:17.520
♪ Like your rush of passion toward me ♪

16:18.080 --> 16:23.170
♪ A toast to our romantic encounter ♪

16:23.200 --> 16:25.200
♪ I am here only for you ♪

16:23.360 --> 16:25.220
Having gained more and more
along the journey,

16:25.220 --> 16:28.480
♪ Even though I know
tremendous danger lies ahead ♪

16:25.630 --> 16:28.550
I've completed the structure
of the caltrop fireball.

16:28.550 --> 16:29.960
The biggest problem now

16:28.640 --> 16:33.090
♪ If you could fill the empty spaces
in my memories ♪

16:30.440 --> 16:32.500
lies in the ore for making gunpowder.

16:34.440 --> 16:36.900
♪ Only you would stay with me ♪

16:36.920 --> 16:40.170
♪ My heartbeat will never fade ♪

16:40.240 --> 16:43.140
♪ The wishes left unsaid ♪

16:43.160 --> 16:45.890
♪ A love I can't let go ♪

16:44.630 --> 16:46.260
It's colder at night in Beifu
than in Jiankang.

16:46.260 --> 16:48.890
♪ A red thread woven by fate ♪

16:47.630 --> 16:49.480
What is Jiayu doing right now?

16:48.940 --> 16:52.180
♪ Love carries longing through time ♪

16:51.000 --> 16:52.390
Has she reached Mount Cang yet?

16:52.380 --> 16:55.960
♪ To make it come true ♪

16:53.440 --> 16:56.440
How's the development
of the caltrop fireball going?

16:59.880 --> 17:03.520
[Two years later, Lai Lake]

17:01.600 --> 17:02.660
Pass the ball to me!

17:03.120 --> 17:03.840
Over here!

17:04.750 --> 17:05.950
It looks pretty nice.

17:06.030 --> 17:07.310
What is this thing?

17:07.310 --> 17:08.770
I've never seen it before.

17:09.680 --> 17:11.510
Keep it down. Miss Xie said

17:11.960 --> 17:13.349
this was transformed from an immortal.

17:13.349 --> 17:14.720
If you get too loud

17:14.829 --> 17:16.349
and scare the immortal away,

17:16.349 --> 17:18.550
we won't have any grain to eat next year.

17:19.240 --> 17:21.500
It has come to life! The wood is animated!

17:21.880 --> 17:22.829
There's water!

17:23.589 --> 17:24.829
Water's flowing right out of it.

17:24.829 --> 17:25.790
This is amazing.

17:26.200 --> 17:27.310
From now on, you can divert

17:27.310 --> 17:28.790
the mountain streams directly
into the farmland

17:28.790 --> 17:29.960
without fetching water on your own.

17:29.960 --> 17:30.890
Thank you, miss.

17:31.510 --> 17:33.720
Our husbands have all gone
to build the canal.

17:33.720 --> 17:34.680
With this waterwheel,

17:34.680 --> 17:36.920
we won't have to carry water
from the mountain anymore.

17:36.920 --> 17:37.720
That's right.

17:39.920 --> 17:40.680
What is it now?

17:40.680 --> 17:41.200
The Miraculous Craft

17:41.200 --> 17:42.790
offers many more novel devices.

17:42.790 --> 17:44.030
They are absolutely real

17:44.030 --> 17:45.090
and helpful to you.

17:46.920 --> 17:49.200
This device can plow over 20 mu a day,

17:49.510 --> 17:51.110
equaling three strong oxen.

17:51.240 --> 17:52.550
Three oxen?

17:52.550 --> 17:53.680
Sounds incredible.

17:55.480 --> 17:57.400
The bamboo strips and palm leaves
of this rain cape

17:57.400 --> 17:58.960
have undergone special treatment.

17:58.960 --> 17:59.920
I guarantee you won't get wet at all

17:59.920 --> 18:01.580
when you wear it in heavy rain.

18:01.920 --> 18:03.200
Top quality, fairly pricing.

18:03.200 --> 18:04.160
A genuine good deal.

18:04.160 --> 18:05.720
-That impressive?
-This is great.

18:05.720 --> 18:06.720
How amazing.

18:14.830 --> 18:16.350
Oh no, My Lady.

18:17.070 --> 18:17.960
Another explosion.

18:17.960 --> 18:18.960
Why an explosion?

18:23.350 --> 18:24.110
Cui Shao'an!

18:25.640 --> 18:26.370
Cui Shao'an!

18:28.030 --> 18:28.760
Cui Shao'an?

18:28.920 --> 18:29.920
Careful, ladies.

18:32.920 --> 18:33.650
Cui Shao'an.

18:34.110 --> 18:35.700
Did you... get hurt?

18:38.400 --> 18:39.770
Don't overthink it.

18:39.830 --> 18:42.090
She's just concerned about your safety.

18:43.750 --> 18:44.790
It seems this batch of ore

18:44.790 --> 18:45.920
is still not pure enough

18:45.920 --> 18:47.030
to be used for caltrop fireballs.

18:47.030 --> 18:47.640
It's fine.

18:48.240 --> 18:49.440
I'll go look for more.

18:50.110 --> 18:51.160
Who would've known?

18:51.160 --> 18:53.750
The Mr. Cui who never did
physical labor before

18:53.750 --> 18:55.160
is now willing and glad to cross

18:55.160 --> 18:56.920
mountains and hills to collect stones.

18:56.920 --> 18:58.650
If I can restore my father's map

18:58.720 --> 18:59.850
of mineral deposits

19:00.110 --> 19:01.410
and help you produce caltrop fireballs,

19:01.410 --> 19:02.440
it'll be counted

19:03.270 --> 19:04.440
as my atonement for the Cui family.

19:04.440 --> 19:05.840
If your sister knew this,

19:06.110 --> 19:07.840
she would be rather gratified.

19:09.920 --> 19:11.380
I'm setting out right now.

19:11.480 --> 19:12.270
Just as usual,

19:12.270 --> 19:13.240
I'll send you letters

19:13.240 --> 19:15.240
on any updates via carrier pigeons.

19:15.420 --> 19:17.140
No need to rush like this.

19:17.480 --> 19:19.030
I know you're eager to get things done.

19:19.030 --> 19:20.310
The military grain canal
is being built at full speed.

19:20.310 --> 19:21.070
Once it's completed,

19:21.070 --> 19:23.070
the army will head north for battle.

19:23.070 --> 19:24.590
There isn't much time
left for the production

19:24.590 --> 19:25.850
of caltrop fireballs.

19:31.200 --> 19:32.330
Keep yourself safe.

19:46.130 --> 19:49.130
The 78th attempt failed.

19:50.680 --> 19:51.610
Nonetheless...

19:52.920 --> 19:56.590
the ore made great purple-red fireworks.

19:58.790 --> 20:01.920
Suggested usage:
fireworks for the Lantern Festival.

20:03.240 --> 20:04.970
It was not entirely fruitless.

20:05.860 --> 20:07.170
Cheer up, Nanxing.

20:10.920 --> 20:12.720
This mess is yours to handle now.

20:20.350 --> 20:24.080
To my beloved wife Yaoyao,
reading this is like seeing me in person.

20:24.200 --> 20:26.270
The first snow arrived
in the Northern Border early.

20:26.270 --> 20:27.960
Fortunately, I didn't let the court down

20:27.960 --> 20:30.160
by eliminating all the bandits
in the southwest,

20:30.160 --> 20:32.270
and thus clearing a lurking peril for Ye.

20:32.270 --> 20:33.470
I am deeply relieved.

20:34.030 --> 20:35.960
However, the grain canal
is not yet finished.

20:35.960 --> 20:38.490
I'm afraid I can't spend
the New Year with you.

20:38.790 --> 20:39.850
In the next spring,

20:40.590 --> 20:43.720
I will be waiting
in the Northern Border for your return.

20:48.070 --> 20:49.590
People who don't know better would think

20:49.590 --> 20:52.640
it's been ages since Your Ladyship
and His Highness last met.

20:52.640 --> 20:53.720
Didn't His Highness take a detour

20:53.720 --> 20:54.880
to this place to visit Your Ladyship

20:54.880 --> 20:57.140
before setting out to fight the bandits?

20:57.160 --> 20:59.090
That was already three months ago.

20:59.550 --> 21:00.830
Besides, last time we met,

21:00.830 --> 21:02.960
I barely got the time to say much to him.

21:03.720 --> 21:04.790
Fine, if you say so.

21:05.350 --> 21:07.680
My Lady, over the past two years,
you've traveled everywhere

21:07.680 --> 21:09.880
in Ye, looking for proper ore
to make caltrop fireballs.

21:09.880 --> 21:11.960
You've also designed many farming tools

21:11.960 --> 21:13.880
and opened branches
of the Miraculous Craft nationwide.

21:13.880 --> 21:14.960
When there are harvests,

21:14.960 --> 21:16.560
the credit will all go to you.

21:17.550 --> 21:18.200
My Lady,

21:18.240 --> 21:19.970
where is our next destination?

21:27.200 --> 21:29.750
Tian Quan should've paid the debt
three days ago,

21:29.750 --> 21:31.000
yet he has not come.

21:31.880 --> 21:33.940
He's not trying to renege on it, is he?

21:35.750 --> 21:37.830
Everyone's saying
that my husband Tian Quan

21:37.830 --> 21:39.960
embezzled the funds
for building the grain canal.

21:39.960 --> 21:41.110
He couldn't take it

21:42.270 --> 21:43.400
and hanged himself.

21:43.640 --> 21:44.590
What grain canal?

21:44.590 --> 21:48.390
The canal for transporting grain
and forage to the Northern Border.

21:48.590 --> 21:49.110
My Lady,

21:50.110 --> 21:51.570
now that Tian Quan is dead,

21:51.720 --> 21:54.380
I'm afraid we won't be able
to get our money back.

21:54.750 --> 21:56.520
Miss, if you're here to collect the debt,

21:56.520 --> 21:58.520
all I can offer is my worthless life.

21:59.070 --> 22:00.200
If you want it, miss,

22:00.310 --> 22:01.310
then just take it.

22:03.160 --> 22:04.490
What exactly happened?

22:05.000 --> 22:06.400
Weren't all the tenant farmers
and artisans of the village

22:06.400 --> 22:08.640
on the east conscripted
to build the grain canal?

22:08.640 --> 22:09.480
Why would there be embazzlement?

22:09.480 --> 22:11.030
The officials were pressing hard,

22:11.030 --> 22:12.350
so my husband led everyone

22:12.350 --> 22:13.920
to work day and night non-stop.

22:13.920 --> 22:14.920
The job was finally done.

22:14.920 --> 22:17.350
Yet the higher-ups said the funds
for building the canal hadn't arrived.

22:17.350 --> 22:20.550
But who doesn't have their hopes pinned on
this money for the New Year?

22:20.550 --> 22:21.920
Then why did people accuse

22:21.920 --> 22:24.110
your husband of embezzling
the canal construction funds?

22:24.110 --> 22:25.880
I swear to heaven that he didn't!

22:25.880 --> 22:26.720
My husband once

22:26.720 --> 22:28.750
went to the local government
to demand justice.

22:28.750 --> 22:30.070
Not only did he fail to get a single coin,

22:30.070 --> 22:31.800
but he was beaten and sent back.

22:32.680 --> 22:33.340
Besides...

22:33.480 --> 22:34.240
Besides what?

22:34.240 --> 22:36.300
Besides, after my husband came home,

22:36.590 --> 22:38.480
he kept cursing Lord Li, the magistrate,

22:38.480 --> 22:39.270
declaring him to be

22:39.270 --> 22:43.070
a heinous corrupt official who only knows
to flatter his superiors.

22:43.640 --> 22:44.970
Go home with your child.

22:45.070 --> 22:46.400
If there is indeed an injustice,

22:46.400 --> 22:48.350
the Young Lady will seek redress
for everyone.

22:48.350 --> 22:49.270
Thank you, miss.

22:49.270 --> 22:50.270
Thank you so much.

22:59.880 --> 23:00.340
My Lady.

23:01.160 --> 23:02.960
I made inquiries at the local government.

23:02.960 --> 23:04.750
County Magistrate Li Geng
left three days ago

23:04.750 --> 23:05.550
for Jiankang,

23:05.750 --> 23:06.880
as the triennial official evaluation

23:06.880 --> 23:07.880
is about to commence.

23:07.880 --> 23:09.440
He is likely taking advantage
of the New Year

23:09.440 --> 23:10.160
to bribe his way

23:10.160 --> 23:11.360
up and down the ranks.

23:11.960 --> 23:13.270
What an outrage.

23:13.920 --> 23:14.450
Nanxing.

23:14.590 --> 23:15.000
Yes.

23:15.720 --> 23:16.720
Pack up our stuff.

23:16.920 --> 23:17.960
We are going back to Jiankang.

23:17.960 --> 23:18.510
Got it.

23:24.160 --> 23:25.620
Little trinkets for sale!

23:26.110 --> 23:27.000
Trinkets for sale!

23:27.000 --> 23:28.130
Come and take a look!

23:28.240 --> 23:29.370
It's been two years.

23:29.750 --> 23:32.410
Jiankang has become
more bustling than before.

23:34.200 --> 23:37.070
It's said that Prince Qi is very popular
with the people.

23:37.070 --> 23:39.000
"A dark eagle soars out of Mount Qi,

23:39.200 --> 23:40.800
bringing in a year of peace."

23:41.640 --> 23:42.830
It's a compliment to Prince Qi

23:42.830 --> 23:44.630
for his excellence governance.

23:45.270 --> 23:46.000
I know.

23:46.550 --> 23:47.270
Everyone

23:48.160 --> 23:50.030
hopes for peace and prosperity.

23:53.310 --> 23:53.750
Look.

23:54.110 --> 23:55.170
Isn't that Li Geng?

23:57.350 --> 23:58.240
Yes, exactly.

23:58.310 --> 23:58.840
Let's go.

24:00.350 --> 24:01.880
Bravo! Bravo!

24:01.130 --> 24:03.130
[County Magistrate, Li Geng]

24:03.590 --> 24:05.550
I heard that once corrupt officials
from all over enter Jiankang,

24:05.550 --> 24:07.550
they'd buy a calligraphy painting
from Guanhai House

24:07.550 --> 24:08.910
and give it as a gift.

24:09.400 --> 24:11.270
Those who receive paintings will sell them

24:11.270 --> 24:13.070
back to Guanhai House for money.

24:15.000 --> 24:17.000
It's practically an industry then.

24:17.160 --> 24:18.790
Look, Li Geng is holding a painting.

24:18.790 --> 24:20.350
It seems he's going to meet the one

24:20.350 --> 24:23.440
manipulating the buying
and selling of official posts.

24:23.440 --> 24:24.110
Perfect.

24:24.440 --> 24:26.070
Let's find out the vermin of the court

24:26.070 --> 24:27.730
and root them out altogether.

24:29.240 --> 24:30.860
[Xiyue Restaurant]

24:32.680 --> 24:33.110
Wait.

24:34.030 --> 24:36.430
Why did he enter Xiyue Restaurant instead?

24:37.510 --> 24:39.200
Come on, let's go get changed.

24:40.030 --> 24:42.590
Thereafter, the saying began to spread—

24:42.640 --> 24:46.970
"When the Phoenix Heart Tokens appear,
peace shall be restored in the world."

24:48.240 --> 24:49.590
Are you from Youzhou?

24:51.240 --> 24:53.110
I am the magistrate of Pingjiang County,

24:53.110 --> 24:54.310
Yueyang Prefecture.

24:54.880 --> 24:55.480
What about you?

24:55.480 --> 24:57.070
-I'm from Changping County.
-Look.

24:57.070 --> 24:59.000
-There was a locusts disaster last year.
-This one's nice.

24:59.000 --> 25:01.240
I even sold my ancestral house
to scrape together

25:01.240 --> 25:02.070
some silver,

25:02.310 --> 25:04.750
hoping to smoothen my way
through the triennial evaluation.

25:04.750 --> 25:05.880
Did you not buy a painting?

25:05.880 --> 25:06.830
I heard that without a painting,

25:06.830 --> 25:07.880
one doesn't even get to meet the inspector

25:07.880 --> 25:09.510
or the state and county
personnel appraisers.

25:09.510 --> 25:10.970
I bought a painting. I did.

25:11.680 --> 25:12.510
That one is it.

25:13.310 --> 25:15.110
It cost me 5,000 taels of silver.

25:15.350 --> 25:16.480
Five thousand taels?

25:16.480 --> 25:17.070
No easy task, really.

25:17.070 --> 25:19.350
What kind of painting
could cost that much?

25:19.350 --> 25:20.270
This is a bribe.

25:21.400 --> 25:22.640
I made it! I made it!

25:23.070 --> 25:24.130
The inspector said

25:24.200 --> 25:25.880
I performed extraordinarily
in the past three years

25:25.880 --> 25:28.610
and that I'd at least get
one "Excellent" rating!

25:29.160 --> 25:30.680
Congratulations!

25:30.680 --> 25:31.510
-Congratulations!
-Thank you.

25:31.510 --> 25:33.750
Magistrate of Pingjiang County,
Yueyang Prefecture!

25:33.750 --> 25:34.510
It's my turn.

25:34.920 --> 25:35.960
Good luck to you!

25:36.240 --> 25:37.510
Wish you success!

26:00.240 --> 26:01.570
Greetings, Inspector.

26:01.880 --> 26:04.550
I am the Magistrate of Pingjiang County,
Yueyang Prefecture.

26:04.550 --> 26:07.070
Pingjiang County had a good harvest
last year.

26:07.070 --> 26:09.130
How come you only offer 12,000 taels?

26:09.720 --> 26:11.050
How dare he ask for more.

26:12.960 --> 26:13.550
Speak up.

26:14.160 --> 26:16.420
What rating would you like me to give you?

26:17.160 --> 26:18.880
If I ask for an "Excellent"
in all three categories...

26:18.880 --> 26:22.340
That will take more than this painting
of Snow on Spring River.

26:26.680 --> 26:27.550
Xiao Wuyi?

26:30.920 --> 26:31.880
Why is it you?

26:32.110 --> 26:33.440
It should be me asking you that.

26:33.440 --> 26:34.750
Why are you messing things up here?

26:34.750 --> 26:35.510
Didn't you tell me

26:35.510 --> 26:36.790
you were off to fight bandits?

26:36.790 --> 26:38.320
How are you an inspector...

26:41.000 --> 26:42.750
So you're the one
taking bribes through paintings?

26:42.750 --> 26:44.310
Why do you need so many of them?

26:44.310 --> 26:45.310
Xiao Wuyi, you...

26:47.400 --> 26:48.070
Hey, what did you just do?

26:48.070 --> 26:49.530
Why did you smash that cup?

26:53.880 --> 26:55.480
The second floor is secured.

26:56.070 --> 26:57.400
Wuyi, why did you...

27:06.400 --> 27:07.200
Jiayu?

27:07.550 --> 27:08.880
What are you doing here?

27:09.880 --> 27:10.740
Your Highness.

27:11.830 --> 27:12.760
Greet him again.

27:16.750 --> 27:17.400
Father.

27:18.480 --> 27:19.740
That's is more like it.

27:43.680 --> 27:45.340
W-What does this stroke mean?

27:45.790 --> 27:46.920
It means two copies,

27:46.960 --> 27:47.920
referring to two identical

27:47.920 --> 27:50.050
calligraphic pieces of Liu Jiang Tie.

27:50.400 --> 27:51.960
Li Geng is pretty rich then.

27:53.750 --> 27:54.720
The calculation's done.

27:54.720 --> 27:56.160
Altogether 47 officials from various areas

27:56.160 --> 27:57.560
came to the capital city.

27:57.680 --> 27:59.030
The money paid as bribes
under the guise of art works

27:59.030 --> 27:59.960
is about 170,000 taels.

27:59.960 --> 28:00.790
How dare they.

28:01.750 --> 28:03.480
When I asked them to build the canal,

28:03.480 --> 28:05.000
they complained
about being poor all the time.

28:05.000 --> 28:06.590
But they sent
170,000-tael-worth gifts without hassle

28:06.590 --> 28:08.450
for the performance evaluation.

28:08.480 --> 28:09.590
Some officials they are.

28:09.590 --> 28:11.320
What do you plan to do with them?

28:11.350 --> 28:12.200
Among these people,

28:12.200 --> 28:13.680
many are from humble origins
and were promoted

28:13.680 --> 28:15.030
by you after the reform began.

28:15.030 --> 28:17.030
Send them all to the Ministry of Justice.

28:17.030 --> 28:20.400
Wuyi, absolutely clear water
is no habitat for fish.

28:20.790 --> 28:21.990
This is officialdom,

28:22.440 --> 28:23.570
not a military camp.

28:23.960 --> 28:27.110
The Beifu Reform has been going smoothly
over these two years.

28:27.110 --> 28:28.790
It is first due to
the concession of noble families,

28:28.790 --> 28:31.650
and second to these officials
from humble origins,

28:31.830 --> 28:33.960
who have done a lot of real work for you.

28:34.200 --> 28:35.680
If you have all of them punished,

28:35.680 --> 28:37.720
I'm afraid others will be disheartened.

28:37.720 --> 28:40.250
You'd hate to be an isolated minister,
right?

28:41.440 --> 28:42.590
Then investigate each of them.

28:42.590 --> 28:44.640
Those who sold
their ancestral houses will be exempted.

28:44.640 --> 28:46.000
Give the money back to them
and chase them away.

28:46.000 --> 28:47.590
Those who are found
to have imposed exorbitant taxes,

28:47.590 --> 28:48.440
embezzled disaster relief funds,

28:48.440 --> 28:49.640
or fraudulently claimed
canal building funds

28:49.640 --> 28:50.640
will have to cough up

28:50.640 --> 28:52.370
every tael of silver they took,

28:52.400 --> 28:53.720
and be sent to the Ministry of Justice.

28:53.720 --> 28:54.960
All illicit gains must be confiscated.

28:54.960 --> 28:56.310
The grain canal building
is short of funds.

28:56.310 --> 28:57.960
If we wait for the court
to allocate funds,

28:57.960 --> 28:59.160
I'm afraid the canal can't be finished

28:59.160 --> 29:00.360
even in the next year.

29:01.110 --> 29:01.640
Got it.

29:02.920 --> 29:03.380
Hold on!

29:04.400 --> 29:05.750
Don't forget about that guy named Li Geng.

29:05.750 --> 29:06.400
It was he who embezzled

29:06.400 --> 29:07.790
the pay
for the workers building the canal.

29:07.790 --> 29:08.350
To add to that,

29:08.350 --> 29:09.680
he caused a man's death.

29:10.070 --> 29:11.670
You must not let him get away.

29:19.310 --> 29:20.550
I misinterpreted your action.

29:20.550 --> 29:21.350
My apologies.

29:21.680 --> 29:23.550
I thought you were that corrupt inspector,

29:23.550 --> 29:25.750
but it turned out
you were on a sting operation.

29:25.750 --> 29:26.680
Well, you see...

29:29.720 --> 29:30.790
I'm so tired

29:30.790 --> 29:32.550
from that lengthy journey today.

29:32.550 --> 29:34.310
I also helped catch
many corrupt officials.

29:34.310 --> 29:36.000
It's getting late.

29:36.310 --> 29:36.920
Father,

29:36.940 --> 29:38.680
I'd like to go and get some rest now.

29:38.680 --> 29:40.740
I will come greet you again tomorrow.

29:41.070 --> 29:42.720
Xie Jiayu, stop running!

29:43.350 --> 29:45.270
You didn't even recognize
the accounting symbols just now.

29:45.270 --> 29:46.030
How could you?

29:46.030 --> 29:46.890
Come back here!

29:47.350 --> 29:48.350
Xie Jiayu!

29:53.110 --> 29:54.440
Xie Jiayu,

29:54.590 --> 29:56.240
I sent over so much pear blossom candy

29:56.240 --> 29:58.440
so as to encourage you to practice hard.

29:58.510 --> 30:01.480
But you actually tricked me
by having Nanxing do all the accounting.

30:01.480 --> 30:02.270
At this rate,

30:02.270 --> 30:03.200
how are you going to handle

30:03.200 --> 30:05.550
the finances of Prince Jing'an's Mansion
in the future?

30:05.550 --> 30:06.680
Yuanji,

30:07.110 --> 30:09.110
Nanxing's here to help, isn't she?

30:10.830 --> 30:12.240
All Nanxing can do is render some help.

30:12.240 --> 30:13.960
You must learn
how to do the calculation yourself.

30:13.960 --> 30:14.960
Well, you're also

30:14.960 --> 30:16.820
here to help, aren't you, Yuanji?

30:19.070 --> 30:21.320
Every year I propose to
hand the accounts over to you,

30:21.320 --> 30:22.510
yet you always make excuses to dodge it.

30:22.510 --> 30:23.480
When the next year begins,

30:23.480 --> 30:25.680
I'll have to return to Yuxi Prefecture
with the He family.

30:25.680 --> 30:28.080
Let's see how long
you can keep avoiding it.

30:37.830 --> 30:38.680
Yuanji,

30:39.750 --> 30:41.070
could you please stay?

30:42.920 --> 30:44.580
So you did all that on purpose?

30:45.170 --> 30:45.850
I...

30:48.680 --> 30:49.680
Silly girl,

30:50.290 --> 30:52.020
I also yearn to live my own life.

30:53.030 --> 30:55.630
Now, things in the He family
have settled down.

30:55.920 --> 30:58.050
I finally get a chance
to go see the outside world

30:58.050 --> 30:59.100
just like you do.

31:00.110 --> 31:01.550
Being constrained by the He family first,

31:01.550 --> 31:02.950
and then the Xiao family,

31:03.160 --> 31:04.590
I was never myself.

31:06.480 --> 31:07.350
This time,

31:07.590 --> 31:09.520
I'd like to be my real self for once.

31:14.000 --> 31:14.880
Well...

31:15.110 --> 31:16.510
Is Mr. Liu going with you?

31:24.240 --> 31:25.110
Actually,

31:25.130 --> 31:26.480
I think Anmin is better.

31:27.110 --> 31:28.670
If you chose him,

31:28.960 --> 31:29.550
then we can

31:29.550 --> 31:31.750
spend every day together in the future.

31:32.750 --> 31:34.010
You're hoping for that

31:34.160 --> 31:37.160
so you can avoid
learning accounting forever, right?

31:40.350 --> 31:41.450
Why does constant parting

31:41.450 --> 31:43.050
have to be part of growing up?

31:46.160 --> 31:47.420
Rest assured, Yuanji.

31:47.440 --> 31:48.840
I'll try my best to learn.

31:57.680 --> 31:59.730
The Eastern Palace summons
the Heir and Lady Xie.

31:59.730 --> 32:00.960
His Highness is waiting now.

32:00.960 --> 32:03.760
The Eastern Palace learned of your return
so soon?

32:20.920 --> 32:21.850
We've parted for two years.

32:21.850 --> 32:23.020
Why never say a word about your return?

32:22.820 --> 32:24.230
[Chief Eunuch of the Eastern Palace,
Feng An]

32:24.200 --> 32:27.030
You just had to make me send an invitation
to Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

32:27.030 --> 32:28.480
See all those memorials behind me?

32:28.480 --> 32:30.200
You're being impeached in every one.

32:30.200 --> 32:32.150
The officials from poor families,
who were promoted by you,

32:32.150 --> 32:33.690
are said to have bribed the inspector.

32:33.690 --> 32:35.350
You knew that long ago, didn't you?

32:35.350 --> 32:37.070
The officials involved were arrested
in Xiyue Restaurant.

32:37.070 --> 32:38.560
Or you couldn't have summoned us
so soon, right?

32:38.560 --> 32:40.290
What was the amount of bribery?

32:40.310 --> 32:42.910
Every item added up to
170,000 taels of silver.

32:43.310 --> 32:45.480
I directed it all
to build the grain canal.

32:45.480 --> 32:47.490
The Department of State Affairs
is too slow with funding.

32:47.490 --> 32:49.830
And it takes you a lot of work
to deal with the ministries.

32:49.830 --> 32:50.550
I'm just helping you

32:50.550 --> 32:52.550
warn the newly promoted officials

32:52.720 --> 32:55.250
from humble origins
to stay on the right path.

32:56.590 --> 32:58.050
As long as you don't fear
offending anyone.

32:58.050 --> 32:58.580
Oh right.

32:59.200 --> 33:00.070
The New Year is approaching.

33:00.070 --> 33:02.730
Do you need to hurry back
to the Northern Border?

33:03.750 --> 33:04.790
Any orders from Your Highness?

33:04.790 --> 33:06.550
What can I possibly order you to do?

33:06.550 --> 33:08.240
I heard your father came back, didn't he?

33:08.240 --> 33:09.240
Since everyone is around now,

33:09.240 --> 33:10.640
we can celebrate the New Year together.

33:10.640 --> 33:11.440
Right, Jiayu?

33:16.950 --> 33:19.030
Mao, is that soft armor?

33:24.590 --> 33:25.750
Premium materials.

33:25.790 --> 33:27.190
Exquisite workmanship.

33:27.680 --> 33:28.940
It's really well made.

33:29.350 --> 33:30.070
Actually,

33:30.550 --> 33:32.750
it's my gift to you for your conferment.

33:37.510 --> 33:38.160
Chan.

33:40.310 --> 33:40.990
Chan?

33:44.590 --> 33:45.510
To be honest,

33:45.900 --> 33:48.340
I've taken Chan as a concubine of mine.

33:57.350 --> 33:58.640
Why did no one tell me
I was to be conferred on

33:58.640 --> 34:00.000
the title of Heir's Consort?

34:00.000 --> 34:01.730
Wuyi already divorced Lady He.

34:02.000 --> 34:03.920
How can the dignified heir
of Prince Jing'an

34:03.920 --> 34:05.160
not have a consort?

34:06.880 --> 34:08.360
So, I directly petitioned His Majesty

34:08.360 --> 34:10.000
before asking for your approval

34:10.000 --> 34:12.400
to confer on Jiayu
the title of Heir's Consort.

34:12.400 --> 34:14.280
His Majesty even specially ordered a seal

34:14.280 --> 34:15.360
and a certificate to be made

34:15.360 --> 34:17.290
by the Imperial Works Department.

34:18.670 --> 34:20.110
I haven't even brought it up yet,

34:20.110 --> 34:21.630
and you're already more eager than I am.

34:21.630 --> 34:22.800
After the New Year,

34:22.929 --> 34:24.520
I will make sure there is

34:24.550 --> 34:26.810
a grand conferment ceremony for you two.

34:27.710 --> 34:28.230
Yaoyao,

34:29.190 --> 34:31.310
the mechanical arts
you love studying do not

34:31.310 --> 34:33.310
bring less danger than battle does.

34:33.480 --> 34:34.550
As you get in and out of the workshop,

34:34.550 --> 34:35.610
wearing this armor

34:35.639 --> 34:36.710
can provide some protection.

34:36.710 --> 34:39.360
There's also a calligraphic work
for you two.

34:39.040 --> 34:43.040
[May you a lifetime of happiness]

34:40.440 --> 34:41.280
Consider it

34:41.280 --> 34:42.880
a wedding gift from me to you.

34:53.400 --> 34:55.860
The Heir Consort's conferment ceremony...

34:56.110 --> 34:57.370
It's a serious matter.

34:57.440 --> 34:59.770
Mao should've discussed with us earlier.

34:59.800 --> 35:01.150
Also, little did I expect

35:01.150 --> 35:03.210
Chan to be taken as a royal concubine.

35:03.920 --> 35:05.520
It didn't occur to me either.

35:07.030 --> 35:08.510
Actually, the conferment ceremony

35:08.510 --> 35:10.110
isn't really that big a deal, is it?

35:10.110 --> 35:11.370
How is it not a big deal?

35:11.920 --> 35:13.150
The entire process of it is even

35:13.150 --> 35:15.150
more complicated than a wedding's.

35:16.280 --> 35:17.940
I thought you'd be delighted.

35:18.360 --> 35:20.110
Of course I'm delighted.

35:20.480 --> 35:21.940
It's just a bit too sudden.

35:21.960 --> 35:23.000
Just some rituals performed at home.

35:23.000 --> 35:25.230
They're hardly as complicated
as you think.

35:25.230 --> 35:26.360
What surprised me

35:27.230 --> 35:29.690
was that Yizhi had a seal newly made
and asked

35:31.360 --> 35:34.670
the Inner Court's Rites Directorate
to prepare for the ceremony.

35:34.670 --> 35:35.800
It's actually good.

35:39.230 --> 35:40.490
I promised your mother

35:40.960 --> 35:42.890
not to drag you into the mess I'm in.

35:43.760 --> 35:44.890
I've broken my word.

35:46.550 --> 35:47.920
Now that it's all inevitable,

35:47.920 --> 35:49.920
I must give you the strongest armor.

35:50.030 --> 35:51.920
With that seal
and the official conferment,

35:51.920 --> 35:53.030
everything in Prince Jing'an's Mansion

35:53.030 --> 35:54.480
will be at your command from now on.

35:54.480 --> 35:55.540
No one can hurt you.

35:57.030 --> 35:59.400
In Prince Jing'an's Mansion,
would anyone give me

35:59.400 --> 36:00.660
a hard time except you?

36:03.440 --> 36:04.400
No, I suppose.

36:13.280 --> 36:14.070
Xiao Wuyi,

36:14.760 --> 36:16.440
will you head north for battle soon?

36:16.440 --> 36:17.760
I'm sick of receiving letters from home

36:17.760 --> 36:19.020
for the past two years.

36:19.320 --> 36:20.920
I want to go to Beifu with you.

36:35.400 --> 36:37.110
My face hurts from all that smiling.

36:37.110 --> 36:38.760
You think the guests were too many?

36:38.760 --> 36:42.480
They were just a few soldiers' families,
coming to offer New Year's greetings.

36:42.480 --> 36:43.540
It is finally over.

36:44.110 --> 36:46.170
I have serious business to attend to.

36:46.510 --> 36:47.840
What serious business?

36:49.360 --> 36:51.280
Xiao Wuyi agreed to let me join the army.

36:51.280 --> 36:53.810
Now, I am Beifu Army's
ordinance supervisor.

36:54.480 --> 36:55.080
Finally,

36:55.400 --> 36:57.360
my skills are needed somewhere.

36:57.840 --> 36:59.240
You're joining the army?

36:59.710 --> 37:01.910
Then what about the household affairs?

37:05.800 --> 37:06.510
My Lady,

37:06.630 --> 37:09.160
I have to manage the Miraculous Craft
for you.

37:09.280 --> 37:11.360
Dear Nanxing, don't be modest.

37:11.710 --> 37:13.110
Thanks to you and Jing Lan,
the Miraculous Craft

37:13.110 --> 37:13.880
could open branches

37:13.880 --> 37:15.590
all over Ye within such a short time.

37:15.590 --> 37:17.800
Someone talented like you
is not to be wasted.

37:17.800 --> 37:18.670
Yuanji,

37:18.690 --> 37:20.000
I'm not being a lazybones.

37:20.000 --> 37:22.360
I'm just assigning the right person
to the right position.

37:22.360 --> 37:24.360
You can always come up with excuses.

37:24.760 --> 37:25.430
This won't do.

37:25.430 --> 37:27.060
I'm just a servant.

37:27.760 --> 37:29.290
So what if you are a servant?

37:30.000 --> 37:30.920
Years ago,

37:30.960 --> 37:32.710
I was just a butcher's daughter.

37:32.710 --> 37:33.480
But now,

37:33.590 --> 37:35.280
I'm a Princess, aren't I?

37:35.800 --> 37:36.590
Mother.

37:37.280 --> 37:38.800
Now that the Heir's Consort
thinks highly of you,

37:38.800 --> 37:40.000
just do your job well.

37:42.800 --> 37:44.270
I swear I will live up to

37:44.360 --> 37:45.760
Your Highnesses' trust.

37:50.210 --> 37:52.940
Mother, you don't think
I'm just messing around?

37:53.510 --> 37:55.400
Yuanji loves studying historical texts.

37:55.400 --> 37:56.630
Ruisheng excels at medicine.

37:56.630 --> 37:57.760
You like mechanics.

37:57.840 --> 37:58.960
Yan Yue practices martial arts.

37:58.960 --> 38:00.760
Nanxing is good at operating business.

38:00.760 --> 38:02.920
As for me, I enjoy feeding chickens

38:02.920 --> 38:03.960
and raising ducks.

38:03.960 --> 38:04.840
We all have things

38:04.840 --> 38:05.920
we'd like to do.

38:06.150 --> 38:08.610
Isn't it nice to leverage
our own strengths?

38:09.190 --> 38:10.070
Let's go have

38:10.070 --> 38:11.030
the New Year's Eve dinner together.

38:11.030 --> 38:11.440
Sure.

38:11.590 --> 38:12.120
Let's go.

38:13.440 --> 38:14.640
Xiao Ziqi, sit tight!

38:16.280 --> 38:17.800
I was out practicing medicine all year

38:17.800 --> 38:18.920
and couldn't discipline you.

38:18.920 --> 38:21.190
So you started causing trouble
here and there.

38:21.190 --> 38:22.880
Do you want to memorize
the acupoint chart again?

38:22.880 --> 38:23.710
Auntie,

38:23.920 --> 38:24.800
help me.

38:24.960 --> 38:25.840
Alright, Sister.

38:25.840 --> 38:27.280
Ziqi says he got the message.

38:27.280 --> 38:28.280
Now, you spoil him

38:28.280 --> 38:29.800
even more than Yuanji does.

38:29.800 --> 38:30.550
Someday,

38:30.580 --> 38:32.280
I'll send you to a school
in the mountains.

38:32.280 --> 38:34.620
The kind where you can't leave
until ten years later.

38:34.620 --> 38:35.230
Come here!

38:37.440 --> 38:38.070
Behave.

38:39.480 --> 38:40.410
Father, Mother,

38:40.630 --> 38:41.760
I'm sorry to be late.

38:42.110 --> 38:44.070
Almost missed the New Year's Eve dinner.

38:44.070 --> 38:46.730
Didn't you say you were busy
with the grain canal

38:46.960 --> 38:49.090
and couldn't come back for the dinner?

38:49.150 --> 38:51.680
I heard there would be
a conferment ceremony.

38:51.920 --> 38:53.520
Wuyi and Jiayu are both back.

38:53.880 --> 38:55.190
As their elder brother,

38:55.190 --> 38:56.480
how could I not come home?

38:56.480 --> 38:57.800
We are all family.

38:57.800 --> 38:59.200
No need for formalities.

38:59.800 --> 39:00.360
Mother,

39:00.880 --> 39:03.150
I noticed last time
that your neck warmer was broken.

39:03.150 --> 39:04.920
So I asked a merchant
from the Western Regions

39:04.920 --> 39:05.880
to buy a new one.

39:06.480 --> 39:07.670
Please try it on, Mother.

39:07.670 --> 39:08.870
Bring it to me, quick.

39:09.400 --> 39:10.930
How thoughtful of you, Yao.

39:13.960 --> 39:15.090
Take a seat already.

39:24.070 --> 39:24.710
Brother.

39:25.190 --> 39:25.760
Yuanji.

39:28.360 --> 39:28.920
Sister.

39:31.320 --> 39:32.880
This year, the Xiao family

39:32.880 --> 39:34.610
is the most complete than ever.

39:34.840 --> 39:35.480
Come on,

39:35.590 --> 39:37.790
let's celebrate the New Year together.

39:37.960 --> 39:40.000
May we have happiness, longevity,
and health.

39:40.000 --> 39:41.000
Happy New Year.

39:41.110 --> 39:42.840
May everyone be well and happy.

39:52.070 --> 39:53.880
Wuyi knows you loves sweet wine, Mother,

39:53.880 --> 39:55.280
so he wrote to me early on,

39:55.670 --> 39:57.630
telling me to prepare some good wine

39:57.630 --> 39:59.150
upon the harvest of grapes,

39:59.150 --> 40:01.670
and make sure it is presented to you
on the New Year.

40:01.670 --> 40:03.530
How considerate of our children.

40:06.960 --> 40:07.480
Good!

40:07.590 --> 40:09.390
Back in the day, your mother here

40:09.550 --> 40:11.360
was a famous wine enthusiast.

40:11.550 --> 40:12.230
Tonight,

40:12.480 --> 40:13.760
let's have many a drink

40:13.760 --> 40:14.960
with your mother!

40:15.070 --> 40:15.550
How about that?

40:15.550 --> 40:16.110
Sure.

40:16.130 --> 40:17.370
I'd like to enjoy such fine wine

40:17.370 --> 40:18.450
with Mother.

40:20.590 --> 40:22.320
Dishes bestowed by the Eastern Palace!

40:22.320 --> 40:26.380
Everyone in Prince Jing'an's Mansion,
receive the dishes and the edict!

40:26.590 --> 40:28.360
By decree of the Eastern Palace,

40:28.360 --> 40:29.550
as the year renews

40:29.550 --> 40:30.840
and a new dawn breaks,

40:31.670 --> 40:34.030
considering your relentless efforts
day and night,

40:34.030 --> 40:35.670
I find your loyalty and diligence
commendable.

40:35.670 --> 40:38.400
Today, I bestow upon you
a feast of delicacies,

40:38.710 --> 40:41.150
named "National Unity

40:41.360 --> 40:42.710
and Family Reunion."

40:42.960 --> 40:45.280
You shall understand
the regard I bear for you,

40:45.280 --> 40:46.840
strive more earnestly in public causes,

40:46.840 --> 40:49.150
and remain of one mind with me,
as ruler and ministers.

40:49.150 --> 40:50.840
As His Highness commands.

40:52.550 --> 40:53.110
Come on in.

40:53.110 --> 40:54.280
Let's continue to drink.

40:54.280 --> 40:54.760
Come on.

40:55.550 --> 40:56.590
The man in black there,

40:56.590 --> 40:58.050
won't you come eat with us?

40:58.360 --> 40:59.510
It's New Year's Eve dinner.

40:59.510 --> 41:00.550
Yes. Mr. Ye Xing,

41:01.030 --> 41:02.030
Her Ladyship said

41:02.150 --> 41:04.110
you should have New Year's Eve dinner
with us.

41:04.110 --> 41:05.000
Leave him alone.

41:05.000 --> 41:06.150
As a royal Shadow Envoy,

41:06.150 --> 41:08.150
he will by no means forget the rules.

41:11.960 --> 41:12.960
You drunk kitten,

41:13.670 --> 41:14.800
it's time to go home.

41:15.480 --> 41:17.410
Why did you come to the horse ranch?

41:18.800 --> 41:21.000
When Anmin gave a neck warmer to Mother,

41:21.070 --> 41:22.880
why did you hide yours?

41:23.360 --> 41:24.760
If I remember correctly,

41:25.030 --> 41:26.110
that was made with the red fox

41:26.110 --> 41:27.770
you hunted on your own, right?

41:28.010 --> 41:30.740
♪ One glance from near stirs my heart ♪

41:28.070 --> 41:30.230
Xiao Wuyi, this is no good.

41:30.590 --> 41:31.800
Really no good.

41:30.960 --> 41:33.510
♪ This fleeting moment ♪

41:32.070 --> 41:33.920
Even if others give her
a hundred neck warmers,

41:33.920 --> 41:35.320
the one presented by you
still has its special meaning.

41:35.210 --> 41:39.220
♪ Tugs the threads woven by fate ♪

41:35.550 --> 41:36.630
Just because someone else
sent her a neck warmer

41:36.630 --> 41:38.480
didn't mean you shouldn't give her one.

41:38.480 --> 41:39.280
Do you hear me?

41:39.390 --> 41:41.390
♪ Bound tight evermore ♪

41:41.510 --> 41:42.310
Do you hear me?

41:43.350 --> 41:46.350
♪ Sharing all the years together ♪

41:44.670 --> 41:45.280
Alright.

41:46.760 --> 41:51.130
♪ Peace I find nowhere but by your side ♪

41:48.630 --> 41:49.630
I got it.

41:51.720 --> 41:54.630
♪ Bear witness with our souls ♪

41:54.070 --> 41:54.800
Xiao Wuyi,

41:55.560 --> 41:58.380
♪ Fear no partings or wax and wane ♪

41:55.840 --> 41:57.770
you need to learn to ask for things.

41:59.900 --> 42:04.240
♪ You know my resolve
to live and die together ♪

42:04.260 --> 42:07.920
♪ Believe in my persistence that
I won't run away ♪

42:08.380 --> 42:12.370
♪ You know me, I'm willing to be
with you till the end ♪

42:12.390 --> 42:16.330
♪ Burn the fire in my heart ♪

42:16.350 --> 42:20.560
♪ Sincere hearts remain as of old ♪
